1 0 0 1 48 551 Tm
(- Character-based chat via server-side prompts and OpenAI chat completions.) Tj
T*
(- 3D avatar preview \(GLB models\) rendered with react-three-fiber/drei.) Tj
T*
(- Firebase Auth \(email/password\) + Firestore for user profiles and chat history.) Tj
T*
(- Chat persistence with pagination \(Firestore queries with limit/startAfter\).) Tj
T*
(- Basic rate limiting \(20 req/min per user\) and concurrency/latency logging.) Tj
T*
(- User profile edit flow \(name/age/bio\) stored in Firestore.) Tj
T*
(- Razorpay order creation API + client-side checkout trigger \(subscription tiers UI\).) Tj
T*
