(How It Works \(Components / Data Flow\)) Tj
T*
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
12 TL
1 0 0 1 48 436 Tm
(- UI routes: / \(home\) -> /avatar/[avatar] \(AvatarRoom: preview + chat panels\).) Tj
T*
(- Preview: AvatarPreviewPanel -> 3D Canvas -> /public/models/*.glb via useGLTF.) Tj
T*
(- Chat client: ChatInterface -> useChat -> saves messages to Firestore, calls /api/chat.) Tj
T*
(- Chat API: POST /api/chat -> rateLimiter + metrics + logger -> OpenAI \(gpt-4o-mini\).) Tj
T*
(- History control: client sends history; server trims to last 20 messages before calling OpenAI.) Tj
T*
(- Persistence: users/{uid}/avatars/{character}/messages \(chat\); users/{uid} \(profile\).) Tj
T*
(- Payments: client opens Razorpay checkout; server creates order at /api/payments/create-order.) Tj
T*
(- Not found in repo.: payment webhook handler implementation \(route.ts is empty\).) Tj
T*
(- Not found in repo.: server-side subscription enforcement for chat limits/features.) Tj
T*
