(1\) Install: npm install) Tj
T*
(2\) Create .env.local with required keys:) Tj
T*
(   - OPENAI_API_KEY) Tj
T*
(   - NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APIKEY, NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTHDOMAIN, NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECTID,) Tj
T*
(     NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGEBUCKET, NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGINGSENDERID,) Tj
T*
(     NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APPID, NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MEASUREMENTID) Tj
T*
(   - RAZORPAY_KEY_ID, RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET, NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID \(if using payments\)) Tj
T*
(   - Not found in repo.: .env.example template) Tj
T*
(3\) Run dev server: npm run dev) Tj
T*
(4\) Open: http://localhost:3000) Tj
T*
